    "Key West Coast Guard Celebrates Birthday Of Service M Vl 31 J 1 1 lai Ub 1 L f t wr 5 4 sbLjWIFIwL 9 LOOKING AHEAD TO ANNIVERSARYLocaI Coast Guardsmen their families and friends en joyed an afternoon of fun and feasting on Friday celebrating the anniversary of the founding of the Coast Guard Actual date of the 169th anniversary is Tuesday August 4 Weather Summary Partly cloudy Scattered showers High today about 88 Low to night about 80 Tomorrows tides High 846 am 959 pm Low 158am 321 pm Winds S to SE 1015 mph VOL LXXX No 183 City Will Sign Voters Under New Law Prizes To Be Given Mon Fiesta Days Sale Is Big With two days of the annual Fiesta Bargain Days under their belts the 28 participating Key West businesses reported today that sales are better than ever and we expect that tomorrow the last day of the event will bring all the last minute shoppers to town as well as a lot more re peat customers said one of the merchants on Duval Street It was pointed out by William Gamble head of the Retail Mer chants Division of the Chamber of Commerce"
